Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.905
So, when I write code,
所以当我写代码时

00:00:01.905 --> 00:00:03.620
sometimes I make mistakes.
有时候我会犯错

00:00:03.620 --> 00:00:05.429
Honestly, this happens to everybody,
说实话每个人都这样

00:00:05.429 --> 00:00:07.439
even the most experienced programmers.
甚至是最有经验的程序员

00:00:07.439 --> 00:00:10.320
Fortunately, pretty much all programming languages
幸运的是所有编程语言

00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:13.019
have mechanisms for detecting our mistakes,
有检测我们错误的机制

00:00:13.019 --> 00:00:16.829
and letting us know about them by displaying error messages.
并通过显示错误消息让我们了解它们 

00:00:16.829 --> 00:00:21.000
Error messages not only draw our attention to the problem,
错误信息不仅引起我们对问题的关注 

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.425
but they also often give us information to help us diagnose the issue and fix it.
但他们也经常给我们提供信息 帮助我们诊断问题并解决问题 

00:00:26.425 --> 00:00:29.580
For instance, Python will display an error message that
例如  Python 将显示一条错误消息 

00:00:29.579 --> 00:00:32.695
tells you what line an error occurred on,
告诉您发生了什么错误

00:00:32.695 --> 00:00:35.575
and what kind of error took place.
发生了什么样的错误

00:00:35.575 --> 00:00:38.265
You'll see a message such as name error,
您会看到诸如名称错误之类的消息 

00:00:38.265 --> 00:00:42.460
or syntax error, and it'll always come with a line number.
或者语法错误 它总是会有一个行号 

00:00:42.460 --> 00:00:45.655
Now the line numbers aren't always entirely correct.
现在行号并不总是完全正确 

00:00:45.655 --> 00:00:48.064
Sometimes they're off by one or two,
有时候他们会被一两个人关了

00:00:48.064 --> 00:00:50.659
but they're usually a really good guide to
但他们通常是一个很好的向导

00:00:50.659 --> 00:00:53.625
where to start looking for the error in your code.
在哪里开始查找代码中的错误 

00:00:53.625 --> 00:00:58.015
Up next, we have a piece of code that has a number of bugs in it.
接下来 我们有一条代码 里面有很多虫子 

00:00:58.015 --> 00:00:59.765
As you work with this code,
当你使用这个代码时

00:00:59.765 --> 00:01:02.480
you'll fix the bugs and the line numbers on
你会把虫子和线号修好

00:01:02.479 --> 00:01:06.879
the error messages will guide you to just where you need to put your attention.
错误消息将引导您进入您需要关注的地方 
